channel.title: [PI]Need help changing max item and level amount
channel.description: :confused: Need help changing the max ammount of a stackable item you can hold I want to set it for 100B and also how do I make the max combat level higher instead of 126 I want it high as possible and using an easy method to change it because im new to Project Insanity. I will rep++ you!!

item.title: [PI]Need help changing max item and level amount
item.dc:creator: @adamknightz adamknightz
item.description:
@adamknightz wrote:

[quote=“belhelmiel, post:3, topic:381533”][quote author=adamknightz link=topic=477345.msg3492474#msg3492474 date=1297030958]
Well…one way to get past level 126 is to add summoning to your server. Not sure of any other way. I’d also like to know a good answer to that.

And I don’t think you can rep++ with 9 rep. (I think you need 15…I’m new to Moparscape.)
[/quote] Noo! I don’t have to add that … I had other servers u can change the max skill level…[/quote]

[s]Oh…max skill level. I see how that works.

I’m not sure if this will work…but…first of all…what do you use? A 317? 508?[/s]

Nevermind…I tried it on my server and it didn’t work.
